{"tid":788312,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"爆炸，估牌子","createTime":"2018-08-21T11:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T10:24:28.000Z","uid":59835,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6300d0cdce0c72d3ab72c4b088434b0ea460db","tid":788312,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"iPad 電池爆炸　Apple 阿姆斯特丹分店需暫時關閉<br />\n<br />\n最近蘋果在阿姆斯特丹的分店發生 iPad 電池爆炸，由於擔心顧客與員工吸入對人體有害的化學物質，店內人士需要緊急疏散，分店需要暫時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒《iCulture》報道，在爆炸後，蘋果工作人員把電池移往裝滿沙的容器內。可幸的是，爆炸沒有引致起火，事件中沒人受傷。但三名員工表示呼吸困難，已接受救援人員治療。由於爆炸可能會釋出有害物質，店內的人需疏散，而分店需暫時關閉，好讓消防人尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n以下為消防車趕赴現場的情況。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 : 9to5mac, AS Media<br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/08/20/ipadbatteryexplosioncausedclosedownofapplestore/mobile-phone/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2Fipadbatteryexplosioncausedclosedownofapplestore%2Fmobile-phone%2Famp%2F&d=L%2BH0bQRk4Pi11%2BTj%2ByuzkfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=53ba396f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/08/20/ipadbatteryexplosioncausedclosedownofapplestore/mobile-phone/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"dd7229aa827d9182deefc22fd73a8db4deb1d570","tid":788312,"uid":164092,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"應該係Samsung電"},{"pid":"619bc6372bc838df1f6cb66f207d24eaee64a44a","tid":788312,"uid":158977,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"dd7229aa827d9182deefc22fd73a8db4deb1d570","tid":788312,"uid":164092,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"應該係Samsung電"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"60bcc7e4b14f1792bcc61bac7912f2692b6fcdfa","tid":788312,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}